hao-70-72", "headline": "IT精英", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10324987906", "reply_comment_id": "10323876946", "reply_root_comment_id": "10323876946", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>我知道报警估计没用，我说自己有白血病，躁狂症，住过几次院，晚上去他床上啥都干得出来</p>", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "冯浩", "author_id": "5dd3dd0ee419b186c46a28ee7cab188f", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "li-shi-pei", "headline": "鸟啼花落自春秋", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10324702062", "reply_comment_id": "10324788262", "reply_root_comment_id": "10323876946", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "「私下」还行。证据链在，青旅也有身份信息，警察早抓晚抓有什么区别？晚抓不承认等价于早抓会承认？再退一步，快递员如果第一时间报了警，还有「私下」这一出？快递员连续失职不作为，他的错误就转嫁给收件人了？", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "李世培", "author_id": "ca8de337c35ba89a0de10bf3c9abb479", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "wen-xiang-shi-nu-ren-86-99", "headline": "白日梦想家", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10324676982", "reply_comment_id": "10323876946", "reply_root_comment_id": "10323876946", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "唉，案值多少？你以为会为了这千里追赃？这家伙再犯算谁的，从此不犯了就这么算了，跟讳疾忌医一样，快刀斩乱麻的爽快事，被办成了窝囊事。", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "闻香识女人", "author_id": "46a439f7ed4cbb78db5d2715564bf85f", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10323573181", "reply_comment_id": "10324580760", "reply_root_comment_id": "10323876946", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "[赞同][赞同][赞同]", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "匿名用户", "author_id": "", "author_is_anonymous": true}, {"url_token": "ow-hoff-yu-80-97", "headline": "不承担权利以外的责任，不支付超过价值的价格。", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10395279371", "reply_comment_id": "10323876946", "reply_root_comment_id": "10323876946", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>装着贵重物品的快递，不打电话不事先联系，往地上扔了就走，这快递员还冤枉了？</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "千奇百怪的旅行", "author_id": "7c50274b0b8d5ef6506ea2656ea3ddbb", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "yue-yu-si-shi-nian", "headline": "左蠢右坏", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10325930250", "reply_comment_id": "10323876946", "reply_root_comment_id": "10323876946", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "快递员也有责任，而且开始态度不好。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "越狱四十年", "author_id": "5a618d8f6f98a2e0af0287954c1c7a48", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "ba-ba-ya-46-77", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10324798580", "reply_comment_id": "10323876946", "reply_root_comment_id": "10323876946", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>你知道快递是应当送到收件人手上的么，不然东西丢了就是快递员的责任</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "爸爸呀", "author_id": "9d2ffdec3d69e2e76efe322010ed88db", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "ying-zi-wu-shi-31", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10323577784", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "10323577784", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "真的是垃圾，你当时就报警，所有人看着，证据确凿，他有脸么？结果你最后发现真正责任人在你自己漫不经心下面放跑了，你才想到去找快递员填坑，真的是优柔寡断，理事不清", "like_count": 133, "author_name": "不会水的鱼", "author_id": "52e077264f390a7bb2fe350dc6c09c65", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "ying-zi-wu-shi-31", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10324916224", "reply_comment_id": "10325206678", "reply_root_comment_id": "10323577784", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "有错也不是这么论的，你见过几个人遇到这种事还有避重就轻的处理的？快递小哥是有错，可是他就算有错，也防不住别人偷东西吧，你对待偷东西的态度是明显的处理不当，你应该优先处理偷东西的，如果处理不好你才应该找快递小哥协助处理共同解决，而不是你想着吓唬的方式，你能吓的住？真正吓得住别人的，要么是名声在外不好惹的，要么就是你不都不用亲自开口别人就替你料理了", "like_count": 21, "author_name": "不会水的鱼", "author_id": "52e077264f390a7bb2fe350dc6c09c65", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "chao-da-hai-xian-guo", "headline": "介绍被我吃了。(ﾟ⊿ﾟ)ﾂ", "is_advertiser": false, "c